item.title: Cant portforward for some reason :(
item.dc:creator: @TaF TaF
item.description:
@TaF wrote:

[quote=“pickle boy4, post:2, topic:392925”]I use utorrent, Download it, open it, Go to Option> Preferences> Connection.
You will see “Listening port” and a button that says “random port” to the left of it type 43594. Make sure randomize port each start isn’t checked.[/quote]
I did that, runelocus or Canyouseeme.org doesnt see me basically, doesnt work
